{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 40.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they gave us the donut mix.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, this is the hot oil.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was this wire basket with the grids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you know, you roll it out, and you make the donut shapes and put it in the wire basket and drop it in the burning oil and take it out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, needless to say, that for about a month, I had all kinds of grid shapes on my arm, because I-- I was never-- I was never in a kitchen before with hot-- before that, if there was hot oil in the kitchen, they would have probably told me, stay out.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, I learned how to make donuts real fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I put on a lot of weight real fast from the skeletal condition that I was in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was filling out, because we also had the keys to the basement, where the food was, where they had the cocoa mixture and egg powder mixture and peanut butter mixture.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "None of the-- and none of these things that exist in Hungary ever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so we used to take this in a big cup and kind of mix it together with instant milk and eat it by the spoonful.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[LAUGHING] So this was the diet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is how the whole summer went by.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in the fall, I don't want to get into the details how, but there was this girl who went back to Hungary-- not one of us, but went through there and said she's going back to Hungary because she has a boyfriend there.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She wants to find him and come back and bring him out also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they'll go to America.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she wanted to know would we want to tell her where our family-- where our family lived and their names, because maybe she would try to find out if they are there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we gave it to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we haven't heard from her for a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't believe in this whole thing anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lo and behold, she came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She found her boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She brought her back, and she came to the base just to tell us that I looked for your families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you, Eva, you have nobody left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you, [NON-ENGLISH] you have nobody left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On you, [NON-ENGLISH] have nobody left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you, Aniko, you know, you have-- your father is there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was the only person, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Your father is there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from that moment on, nobody could keep me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they really tried, very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to bring me to America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they'll adopt me, and they'll put me-- put me through art school and all kinds of things, and begged me not to go back to Hungary, because it's big disarray and mess.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the roads are in bad condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's still no mass transportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The trains are not running.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russians are doing terrible things there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But all this went one ear in, the other out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have given me all kinds of things to take with me, you know, like chocolate and cigarettes and cheese and things like that, in a bag.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it took me a couple of weeks, and I went back to Budapest, and I--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like the fall of '45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the fall of '45.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was still in this-- my dream state of totally fearless and trusting that now all-- everything is going to be wonderful.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody who was American, I trusted 100%, the Russians, too-- anybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would go with auto-stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would sleep someplace.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would see a jeep come by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would-- they would pick me up, and they would say, well, I can take you to the next town, but there you have to fend for yourself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they would bring me to the town square and say, you can go in here and ask there and whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everybody was-- white or black, I didn't know the difference anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But everybody was very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember getting to Czechoslovakia, to Pilsen, where they said that from here on, things will be different, because from here on, it's the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So from there on, there were no more rides in jeeps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I got on trains, which were full of Russian soldiers, jammed with Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they said, OK, don't worry, you can lie down and then sleep, and we'll watch over you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I laid down and slept, and they watched over me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's how I went back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had nothing but help from all these soldiers-- American, Russian, anybody-- and kindness.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
